Jenkins is A Tool used to automated your workflow, by the help of the pipeline.
Jenkins also works on Master-WoRKER architecture.
Master used to give the command to Workers adn they worked on that.


---How to connect master to Worker node---

first download jave lang and jenkins-LTS version on master && java-lang on worker.
 
use two server - one as master ,one as worker

~/.ssh on master

ssh-keygen

copy the pub key & and paste it on ~/.ssh worker server 

then , go to jenkins UI and

manage jenkins

add worker node

then, give datails,

add Worker ip on  host-part

add Private-ssh-key to add credentials

then connect it with Jenkins.



